# shebang-with-comment

## Input

```
#!/usr/bin/env mical
# comment
key value

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..41
  DIRECTIVE@0..20
    SHARP@0..1 "#"
    WORD@1..14 "!/usr/bin/env"
    LINE_STRING@14..20
      STRING@14..20 " mical"
  NEWLINE@20..21 "\n"
  COMMENT@21..30
    SHARP@21..22 "#"
    SPACE@22..23 " "
    WORD@23..30 "comment"
  NEWLINE@30..31 "\n"
  ENTRY@31..41
    WORD_KEY@31..34
      WORD@31..34 "key"
    SPACE@34..35 " "
    LINE_STRING@35..40
      STRING@35..40 "value"
    NEWLINE@40..41 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        Directive {
            sharp: SHARP@0..1 "#",
            name: WORD@1..14 "!/usr/bin/env",
            args: LineString {
                string: STRING@14..20 " mical",
            },
        },
        Entry {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@31..34 "key",
            },
            value: LineString {
                string: STRING@35..40 "value",
            },
